snippet.title: Submarine Titans Trailer (1997)
snippet.description:
Very early trailer of Ellipse Studios' underwater RTS game "Submarine Titans".

This trailer is from early 1997 while the game wouldn't actually be released until 2000. At this point in time they were still known as Megamedia Australia, a development arm of the publisher best known for the Megapak budget compilation bundle series.
